Class SwingAdvancedControlInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • controlinterface.iface.AbstractControlInterface
      • controlinterface.swinguiadvanced.control.SwingAdvancedControlInterface
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ControlInterface, GeneralEventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class SwingAdvancedControlInterface
extends AbstractControlInterface
implements GeneralEventListener
    Contains methods for an advaned user interface to almost every functionality of the system.
